{"tid":634694,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"轉工後又後悔了","createTime":"2018-04-19T12:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T08:26:59.000Z","uid":115069,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e8ff2c3c90ac05236b58515d5c1a1f5f5eac3b69","tid":634694,"uid":115069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"原本份工就幾自由 遲到少少 冇野做就早走都得 同事都好好相處 一齊食飯有講有笑 不過就細公司冇乜野學到 但係聽到有份大公司肯請就冇唸咁多狗衝左<br />\n<br />\n岩岩返左大公司幾日 返工時間冇乜彈性8-6 成個office氣氛嚴肅 鬼佬做呀head 同事之間冇細公司咁緊密 好撚大壓力(唔知係同事比定自己比自己) 每日返工都好唔撚開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdbea2d842b1679b35602eec2db53f1c651735b","tid":634694,"uid":37976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:48:36.000Z","msg":"人工高左幾多？"},{"pid":"d09bc3ff1de0cdb4d73d76f767d0633cb3ba2c07","tid":634694,"uid":115069,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"8cdbea2d842b1679b35602eec2db53f1c651735b","tid":634694,"uid":37976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:48:36.000Z","msg":"人工高左幾多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"本身出黎做左半年only, 新果份高10幾%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987b7a917da389750f7e8129bcff2cb0d807fff5","tid":634694,"uid":43042,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:50:53.000Z","msg":"大公司好處係唔洗驚冇野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做細公司真係可以hea到仆街"},{"pid":"395d6264875495986cc213b131eb9eb7d326b9a8","tid":634694,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"未習慣姐"},{"pid":"81d3a2f5c8fb0d9d9e6be7834a5201f19f384370","tid":634694,"uid":115069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"395d6264875495986cc213b131eb9eb7d326b9a8","tid":634694,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"未習慣姐"},